{{Quote|My mistress requires your presence in the Narthex Antechamber at once.|[[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]|<ref name="Star Wars Droids: The Protocol Offensive">''[[The Protocol Offensive]]''</ref>}}
The '''Narthex Antechamber''' was an apparently nonexistent room within [[Krax's castle]].

Around [[6 BBY/Legends|5.5 BBY]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] sent off two guards to the Narthex Antechamber in order to assist his mistress, [[Stigrit Krax]]. However, this was actually a ruse to steal a [[Speeder bike/Legends|speeder bike]] and rescue [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[Larka Nimondro]]. While the guards did not know where or what the antechamber was, they did not allow the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] to know and went off in search of the room.

